WEBVTT

00:11:28.442 --> 00:11:30.372
So what's the secret?

00:11:30.372 --> 00:11:31.896
Well, he told me.

00:11:31.896 --> 00:11:38.532
He said the key is
he never took sugar with his tea.

00:11:38.532 --> 00:11:41.593
I said, what has that
got to do with anything?

00:11:41.593 --> 00:11:44.759
Well, he said, his party starts
getting ready for the next election

00:11:44.759 --> 00:11:46.300
the day after the last one,

00:11:46.300 --> 00:11:50.281
and he spends all day every day
meeting with voters in their homes,

00:11:50.281 --> 00:11:52.863
in their wedding parties,
circumcision ceremonies,

00:11:52.863 --> 00:11:55.818
and then he meets with his colleagues
to compare notes.

00:11:55.818 --> 00:12:00.384
With that many meetings every day,
with tea offered at every one of them,